longBusinessSummary: Adani Total Gas Limited engages in the city gas distribution business in India. The company supplies piped natural gas and compressed natural gas to the domestic, commercial, industrial, and transportation sectors. It also provides biogas, biofuel, biomass, LCNG, HCNG, EV, and hydrogen, as well as value-added services related to city gas distribution business. In addition, the company manufactures various equipment related to city gas distribution business. The company was formerly known as Adani Gas Limited and changed its name to Adani Total Gas Limited in January 2021. Adani Total Gas Limited was incorporated in 2005 and is headquartered in Ahmedabad, India.
